formThreeBId.notesToCertificate: Land cost estimation is provided by mgmt as there is development agreement for this project. The Promoter has opened RERA Bank Account , but the transactions are made in current account only. Moreover the promoter has multiple projects running in the same tally and promoter has not maintained costing project wise, hence to comment  upon incurred and paid cost we have relied upon the total builtup area construction for the project and segregated the same to the total cost.Promoter has received occupancy certificate from the planning authority. for considering incurred and paid cost we have considered creditors mentioned in head "Sundry Creditors", booking deposit received from the project is considered as available under the heads "Adv for Radha Bunglow GST,Adv for Radha Bunglow @ 5%,& Adv for Radha Bunglows" Land cost is taken as provided by mgmt. preparation of financials is responsibility of mgmt, we have not scrutinised tally backup.
